{"tid":215493,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"二戰轟炸機復修飛抵澳門   鄧梓峰中尉：「差啲想上去噠著嚟飛」","createTime":"2017-04-24T12:36:47.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-25T02:48:10.000Z","uid":79563,"like":22,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"cbd2580b1dca0323abd2464282e0c124f68e188e","tid":215493,"uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T12:36:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170424/large/1493031852_49f4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170424%2Flarge%2F1493031852_49f4.jpg&h=1211c60b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170424/large/1493031853_ccb3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170424%2Flarge%2F1493031853_ccb3.jpg&h=671d99bd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一架機齡達77年、曾參與二戰作臨時轟炸機的道格拉斯（Douglas）DC-3雙槳機，3月從瑞士出發展開環球之旅，今日短暫停留澳門機場並開放予傳媒參觀。無論是外殼以至引擎，飛機大部份設備均由出廠沿用至今，負責修復及駕駛的機師Francisco Agullo笑言，現代飛機有自動飛行「兩隻手指就可以操控」，但DC-3靠機械控制，駕駛時必須全神貫注，「幸好我們有兩個機師。」<br />\n<br />\n持小型飛機駕駛執照、曾為皇家香港軍團（義勇軍）中尉的藝人鄧梓峰指出，DC-3為世界和平作出不少貢獻，包括在二戰「諾曼第登陸」時負責空投傘兵，對親眼見到可以飛的DC-3表現興奮，「差啲想上去噠著嚟飛」。 <br />\n<br />\n曾自己裝嵌飛機並完成環球之旅的機師鄭楚衡今日亦到場參觀，坦言一直都想成為乘客登上DC-3，認為這架飛機「相當新淨」。他指DC-3與自己熟悉的現代飛機結構不同，「全部嘢都好新鮮，簡單得嚟又好複雜」。<br />\n<br />\nDC-3由美國道格拉斯公司設計，於1935年首度試飛，翌年起正式投產，因低耗油兼可長距離飛行，廣受當時美國航空公司歡迎。二戰爆發後，DC-3被美軍徵召，其軍用版改稱C-47，另有C-49、C-53等型號，負責運送士兵及物資。<br />\n<br />\n今次展開環球之旅的DC-3編號2204，1940年3月9日完成首航，3日後交付予美國航空公司（American Airlines），並在二次大戰爆發後，於1942至1944年期間加入美國空軍，負責盟軍後勤支援。在其中一次前往格陵蘭的任務中，它曾短暫拆去行李艙門成為臨時轟炸機，目標是搜索並擊沉在附近海域出沒的德軍U型潛艇，但最終無發現敵蹤，亦未有投下任何炸彈。<br />\n<br />\n2008年飛行愛好者兼機師Francisco Agullo，獲瑞士錶廠百年靈支持，從美國私人收藏家手上購得這架古董飛機並進行修復。他指當時飛機因保養得宜狀態不差，但仍要作升級，包括將駕駛室及機艙座位更新為現代標準，以及更換塗裝；因應環球之旅，部份座位被移除用作加大油缸，令最長飛行時間由8小時提升至12小時。<br />\n<br />\n從實物可見，飛機外殼以至整體結構都無改動，停泊時機頭較高，機身明顯傾斜，機艙內的窗戶採用與現代機截然不同的正方設計，並沿用木材作窗框。<br />\n<br />\nFrancisco表示，現代飛機有電腦輔助，笑言「有兩隻手指就可以操控」，但DC-3主要靠機構結構控制，「你的肌肉可以感受整架飛機」，機師駕駛時亦因此需要全神貫注，起飛前需要充足休息，「但幸好我們有兩個機師，可以輪流駕駛」。"},{"pid":"b27c0f8133036c38aab581918207b0b67341813f","tid":215493,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T12:38:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.dailymail.co.uk/i/pix/2008/05_04/Bombers1PA_700x419.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.dailymail.co.uk%2Fi%2Fpix%2F2008%2F05_04%2FBombers1PA_700x419.jpg&h=b1e18641&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://footage.framepool.com/shotimg/qf/936005382-douglas-dc-3-collection-william-wyler-boeing-bomber.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffootage.framepool.com%2Fshotimg%2Fqf%2F936005382-douglas-dc-3-collection-william-wyler-boeing-bomber.jpg&h=02e058ca&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cbce52ecfe6fe712fc2ad91c7d6f0fffeee5a59c","tid":215493,"uid":26506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T12:43:09.000Z","msg":"有冇人咁勁飛過DC-3?"},{"pid":"865d48e681336304312afdbc2821992218e560b6","tid":215493,"uid":92315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T12:44:28.000Z","msg":"國泰城出面嗰架係咪dc3？"},{"pid":"265f6ac523196802b4e010ba1a032a521490da8d","tid":215493,"uid":34838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T12:45:25.000Z","msg":"巴斯光年一飛沖天<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99f115ea541018141bccec169e5c02457fb2a0da","tid":215493,"uid":7840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T12:46:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e34e3157cfcab48b269118e467be2d32b1513e75","tid":215493,"uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T12:47:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>國泰城出面嗰架係咪dc3？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n記憶中, 係<br />\n<br />\n國泰第一部機, 就係退役軍機<br />\n<br />\n創辦人係盟軍退役機師"},{"pid":"79012b8cb672cb6ffd8b5bc66137cc2ca6071c94","tid":215493,"uid":4493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T12:54:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>國泰城出面嗰架係咪dc3？</blockquote><br />\n係 科學館都係"},{"pid":"50e6325d4d6ac446d7f580977f2cbe12e95c4276","tid":215493,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T13:00:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>國泰城出面嗰架係咪dc3？</blockquote><br />\n係 科學館都係</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n分別係, 香港個兩架飛唔起, 只係擺<br />\n<br />\n人地復修既係飛到<br />\n<br />\n日本仔都有整返零戰, 成日做AIR SHOW"},{"pid":"0f345f0ba65fc5e4e5e372a9fa37b9ccbd4cc199","tid":215493,"uid":39092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T13:03:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>國泰城出面嗰架係咪dc3？</blockquote><br />\n係"},{"pid":"dac02e3ab0b30c6037cc508ce4be05f0c74e3a6e","tid":215493,"uid":104148,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T13:07:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://www.weshare.hk/uploads/14356/Il444TUtt8Ft_6PyF9l8Gg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.weshare.hk%2Fuploads%2F14356%2FIl444TUtt8Ft_6PyF9l8Gg.jpg&h=a6ae854f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8cdf8bf993cd16252d6e22f772474e02021a876e","tid":215493,"uid":42820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T13:11:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"http://www.weshare.hk/uploads/14356/Il444TUtt8Ft_6PyF9l8Gg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.weshare.hk%2Fuploads%2F14356%2FIl444TUtt8Ft_6PyF9l8Gg.jpg&h=a6ae854f&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ecc2220ecbf71028f0eca2b11bcada6dba1645a","tid":215493,"uid":76470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T13:11:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"http://www.weshare.hk/uploads/14356/Il444TUtt8Ft_6PyF9l8Gg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.weshare.hk%