moji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12f8c69b5c5ad0da270ee02de63b99082c7fbe8f","tid":215493,"uid":23141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T13:52:50.000Z","msg":"曾為皇家香港軍團中尉<br />\n估唔到輕輕鬆鬆咁把炮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4753205f74af0e1a48254cbf534b95cf57ed45f7","tid":215493,"uid":61292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T14:01:25.000Z","msg":"你冇得同我架DC 鬥鬥鬥鬥鬥"},{"pid":"d6bcaf8107f11fabec1fee23edda7e65fb22b5a9","tid":215493,"uid":31637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T14:05:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"http://www.weshare.hk/uploads/14356/Il444TUtt8Ft_6PyF9l8Gg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.weshare.hk%2Fuploads%2F14356%2FIl444TUtt8Ft_6PyF9l8Gg.jpg&h=a6ae854f&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class